### Goal
Ensure rich output adds negligible overhead, especially in agent/JSON mode.

### Lazy Initialization Strategy
```rust
impl OutputContext {
    pub fn new() -> Self {
        Self {
            mode: Self::detect_mode(),
            console: OnceCell::new(),  // Lazy!
            theme: OnceCell::new(),    // Lazy!
        }
    }

    fn console(&self) -> &Console {
        self.console.get_or_init(|| {
            Console::new()
                .force_terminal(matches!(self.mode, OutputMode::Rich))
        })
    }
}
```

